# plot each sensors full temperature range for all three years of data...
for unique_sensor in tdf.sensor.unique():   
    print('----------------------------------------')
    print('UNIQUE SENSOR --- ', unique_sensor)
    print('----------------------------------------')
    plt.figure(figsize=(20,6))
    sns.lineplot(x = tdf[tdf.sensor == unique_sensor].index, y=tdf[tdf.sensor == unique_sensor]['value_hrf']) 
    plt.show()
